21/* This is the location of the online document giving instructions for
22 reporting bugs. If you distribute a modified version of GCC,
23 please configure with --with-bugurl pointing to a document giving
24 instructions for reporting bugs to you, not us. (You are of course
25 welcome to forward us bugs reported to you, if you determine that
26 they are not bugs in your modifications.) */
27
28const char bug_report_url[] = BUGURL;

30/* The complete version string, assembled from several pieces.
31 BASEVER, DATESTAMP, DEVPHASE, and REVISION are defined by the
32 Makefile. */
33
34const char version_string[] = BASEVER DATESTAMP DEVPHASE REVISION;
35const char pkgversion_string[] = PKGVERSION;
